Package communication.protocols

Interface Summary
Protocol Skeleton of a communication protocol
 

Class Summary
BookingProtocol A protocol used to handle booking transaction messages
CancelBookingProtocol A protocol used to handle booking cancellation transaction messages
CancelPreBookingProtocol A protocol used to handle prebook cancellation transaction messages
ClusterHelloProtocol A protocol used to relay the ClusterInfo to a requesting node
DataRequestHandlingProtocol<DATA> A protocol to handle DataRequestMessages and reply with a DataRequestReplyMessage
DataTransferHandlingProtocol<DATA> Protocol to handle a data transfer
HelloProtocol A protocol handling hello messages and registering them
LoopbackProtocol A simple protocol to send back the received message to the other party
MessagePrinterProtocol A simple Protocol to print out the received message (no reply created)
PreBookingProtocol Protocol to handle requests to pre-book seats
ProtocolControlledMessenger A networking interface which uses Protocols to handle Messages
RequestHandlingProtocol A generic protocol to handle requests
SectionStatusUpdateRequestHandlingProtocol A protocol to handle section status update requests
TransactionExecutionProtocol<KEY,VALUE,RETURN> A protocol to handle incoming Transaction requests and execute them
TransactionExecutionReplyProtocol<KEY,VALUE,RETURN> A protocol handling messages detailing the result of a transaction on the remote node
TransactionTerminationProtocol<KEY,VALUE,RETURN> A protocol used to instruct a node to either commit or abort a Transaction
TransactionTerminationReplyProtocol<KEY,VALUE,RETURN> A protocol handling the final transaction message from a remote node
